    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 at MRL 2. Predicted RH values remain below 1.0 across all five operating points, satisfying the acceptance criterion. The assessment team notes that the validation evidence is based on high-fidelity numerical simulation benchmarked against published experimental data; the simulation approach is judged to provide equivalent confidence to a dedicated bench experiment given the calibrated damage model and demonstrated GCI compliance. On this basis, the credibility of the CFD hemolysis model for the stated COU is accepted.",
